{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act47side", "eventName": "未許之地", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "UR-4", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "晴空亂流", "storyInfo": "梅希亞一面幫高登引開娜斯提，一面幫衰老的女妖找人。隨後，娜斯提收到了那支丟失的骨筆的殘片。另一邊，高登押著費爾南和奧克里，取道萊茵生態園的地下運輸通道，試圖將違禁品運出園區。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$monastery_sad_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_hotel", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"type": "bg", "id": "68_g2_groundparkstreet_n", "from": 0.0, "to": 0.8, "duration": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_highheeledshoe_carpet_fts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，我來晚了。今天的工作有點忙。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梅、梅希亞……請你……", "name": "疲憊的女聲"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我需要……想起，更多……", "name": "疲憊的女聲"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.5, "duration": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您的情況很特殊。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您的記憶像是枯枝上僅存的敗葉，拂去灰塵或許能令它們恢復些許色澤，但太過用力，只會造成傷害。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#9$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.5}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我甚至不該去撥弄它們的，若不是……", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#9$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#9$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.5}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，拂哀菈女士。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#9$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我需要……知道，需要……想起。", "name": "拂哀菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#9$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#8$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.5}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "離開家鄉之後的回憶對您來說並不愉快，但如果您堅持……那就閉上眼睛吧，我們繼續嘗試。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#8$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_bowl_smash", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有些費力地，梅希亞把她總帶在身邊的那台老舊的幻燈機搬上了桌子。"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_mgcdevcstartp", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隨著她指尖滑動，玻璃幻燈片落入卡槽，一幅陌生的景象籠罩了女妖衰老的身軀。"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "44_g4_towerroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"type": "bg", "id": "44_g7_ludwigsuniv_inside", "from": 0.8, "to": 0.0, "duration": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_signlntrfrnc", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_tvnoise", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.5, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_filmprojection"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_filmprojection_loop", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "delay": 0.5}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我記得，那個地方。", "name": "拂哀菈"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊塔尼亞？", "name": "梅希亞"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她……提過。", "name": "拂哀菈"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那裡，高塔……鐐銬，血。", "name": "拂哀菈"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "緩慢地，模糊地，一段記憶在幻燈機投射出的背景上暈開。梅希亞辨認出一具衰老的身軀被鎖在牆邊，幾個穿著長袍的人影進進出出。"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一些血的氣味，一段可怖的旋律，一些術式的痕跡。"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊塔尼亞的高塔，您被囚禁在那裡過？……作為實驗對象？", "name": "梅希亞"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "若不是一位巫妖出手相助，您差點就被埋葬在高塔術師的書頁之下。", "name": "梅希亞"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_button", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g5_laterano_chapelout", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聖城的安魂教堂，您在那裡為人送葬？是為您流落在外的同胞，還是為您族群的……仇敵？", "name": "梅希亞"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但那些天使並不領情，對嗎？他們的葬禮上需要的是歡笑，而不是您的……哀哭。", "name": "梅希亞"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您差點被戍衛隊逮捕。", "name": "梅希亞"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_button", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g2_edgeofbase", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您來到哥倫比亞……是橫穿了整片拓荒地，甚至……骸骨荒原？", "name": "梅希亞"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那片野獸都不敢踏足的、被風沙切割得千瘡百孔的土地？", "name": "梅希亞"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_hotel", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#5$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您最後還是來到了這裡。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#5$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼，偏偏是這座園區？您是來尋找什麼……", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#7$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2035_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡，這裡也有……樹。", "name": "拂哀菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2035_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2035_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡的樹，也在枯萎、腐敗……", "name": "拂哀菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2035_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2035_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "枯萎、腐敗。", "name": "拂哀菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2035_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#15$1"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來如此。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#15$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#15$1"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡的確有一座生態園，它也確實剛剛發生過一場令人不忍卒睹的事故，枯萎、腐敗，如您所說。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#15$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而那座生態園的主人……", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#11$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是另一位女妖。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#11$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許，您認得這個嗎？", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#11$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那支在生態園釀成大禍，後來又被高登收繳的骨筆，就這樣潔白無辜地躺在梅希亞的手中。"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2035_1#4$1", "duratin": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……她。", "name": "拂哀菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2035_1#4$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2035_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的氣息……她在。", "name": "拂哀菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2035_1#4$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，您是來找人的。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2035_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想……我想見她……", "name": "拂哀菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2035_1#3$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_cherunder_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$escape_intro", "key": "$escape_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#8$1", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0", "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0", "duration": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用把身子壓得這麼低，奧克里，你背上的施術裝置已經歪了。", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡可是萊茵生命的地下通道，說不定連牆壁裡都有奈米監聽器！", "name": "奧克里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再說了，我們還要小心園區的報警系統……既然是幫高登長官辦事，為什麼還要躲著警衛隊？", "name": "奧克里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你覺得有幾個下屬能得到他的完全信任？", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……", "name": "奧克里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看守電梯的小警衛都有可能是哪位大人物的第三隻眼睛。要是出了差錯，牽扯出的問題可能還比這幾箱違禁品嚴重許多。", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我們這兩個沒有相關利益的外來人，反倒是替他“銷贓”的最佳人選？", "name": "奧克里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯。", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#7$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過有一個問題我確實想不通。", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？", "name": "奧克里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "做事的人有了，接應的人也安排好了，那躺在辦公室裡餵鱗獸、聽聽音樂不是更好嗎？", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長官，親自過來監工可是會惹上麻煩的啊？", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1", "duratin": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，我當然是來為我的小傢伙們送行的！", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#2$1", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？", "name": "奧克里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#2$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#7$1", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別隨便亂晃，蠢貨，源石技藝還原裝置的保護殼差點就撞到牆了！我跟你們說過，要把這批貨看得比自己的命還重要。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#7$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#2$1", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然！", "name": "奧克里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#2$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那您也一定記得，要是我們兩個把這些“小傢伙們”安全送出去，管好了自己的嘴——", "name": "奧克里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#3$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的帳一筆勾銷。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#3$1", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太好了！", "name": "奧克里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別掉以輕心。娜斯提不願撤出生態園，寧願面對滿牆失敗品也要繼續研究，甚至晝夜不停。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#4$1", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "50,0", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4214_cairn_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以她現在就在我們的頭頂上？我好像聽到她的腳步聲了……", "name": "費爾南"}, "figure_art": "avg_4214_cairn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用擔心，梅希亞會幫我們解決這個小問題。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小梅，小梅！", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#9$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"maskid": "group_interclude_vertical_common", "size": "290,760", "style": 0.0, "switch": "true", "offset": "250,0", "channel": 3.0, "tsfrom": "0,1", "tsto": "1,1", "tsduration": 0.5}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "type": 3.0, "slot": "m", "switch": "true", "pfrom": "280,0", "pto": "280,0", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "switch": "true"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……啊，聽得到，高登長官。", "name": "梅希亞"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "switch": "false"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你那邊怎麼樣？要是計劃失敗，就算是出面硬拖，也一定要拖住娜斯提。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "switch": "true"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請您放心，長官。", "name": "梅希亞"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就是因為我的疏忽，所以才出了那麼多意外……", "name": "梅希亞"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一定會盯緊娜斯提主任，確保她離開萊茵生態園，為你們爭取盡可能多的時間。", "name": "梅希亞"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "switch": "false"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很好。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#3$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "clear": "true", "tsfrom": "1,1", "tsto": "0,1", "tsduration": 0.5}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "interlude", "attributes": {"channel": 3.0, "clear": "true"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1", "focus": "l", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看吧，關鍵時刻連小梅都變得這麼可靠了。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1", "focus": "l", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們兩個給我認真一點，快到運輸口了。", "name": "高登"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2034_1#1$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "知道了，長官。", "name": "奧克里"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1000_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費爾南小姐的聽覺真是敏銳啊。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#1$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梅希亞小姐，您的身分可能會暴露，需要我們以緊急管理監督協會的身分出面干預嗎？", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#15$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把梅蘭德的招牌用在更重要的地方吧，高登長官的秘書是個很好用的幌子，我這裡不用費心。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#15$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#13$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "報告情況。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#13$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "根據二組白天收集到的情報，萊茵的技術人員確實撤出了實驗區，只有娜斯提主任和一名助手出入這個場館，只不過……", "name": "梅蘭德特工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#13$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她待在這裡的時間長到令人費解。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#13$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……是的。", "name": "梅蘭德特工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，身為您的小隊成員，我們應該更信任您的判斷，萊茵生命可能確實在展館地下藏了什麼東西。", "name": "梅蘭德特工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#14$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用道歉，監視各家科技公司本來就是我的任務。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#14$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我們要進一步搜查，娜斯提主任那邊……", "name": "梅蘭德特工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2046_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心，照我的計劃，如果一切順利，保守估計能為我們爭取二十分鐘的調查時間。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#6$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2037_1#17$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我準備了一份，她無法拒絕的禮物。", "name": "梅希亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2037_1#17$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "38_g5_rhinelab_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$keyboard"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_aircraftalarm", "volume": 0.2}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1", "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "duration": 0.8, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊啊——！", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#12$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再來一次。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "娜斯提主任，生態園和浮空種植單元的程式就是用這套系統實現的？", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然隔空控制物體是女妖之所長，但放棄以聲音作為媒介，將咒言封存在模組之中，依靠自循環修復漏洞，這簡直就是劃時代的發明！", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是全由咒言驅動……", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#3$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "少看一些純屬臆測的論文，斯凱。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "包含我在內的大多數人對女妖的瞭解有限，我聽說她們棲居在河谷之中，很少離開……", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來哥倫比亞歷練之前，你也待在那裡？", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我最初的記憶來源於卡茲戴爾，後來同族收養了我，將我帶回了河谷。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是個怎樣的地方？", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#5$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "與世無爭的好地方。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "河流邊的草地和叢林茂密，花朵不敗、果實不落。不說天災，連雨水都極少侵擾它的安寧。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然如此，你為什麼要走呢？", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼晚了，是誰？", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#5$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-200,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5, "focus": "l", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "主、主任，快點過來！", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是不是你遺失的那支骨筆？", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g4_corridor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.2, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是那支骨筆……的一部分。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "娜斯提和斯凱腳邊，被切斷的錐形筆尖在地上來回滾動。"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太過分了……", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "生態園的事故不是意外也不是誰的惡作劇，一切都是有備而來。針對你，或是針對萊茵。", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#11$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有一種方法可以把事情弄清楚。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（薩卡茲語）指引。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#2$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_magic_1", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.7, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.4, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.2, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "娜斯提手中的殘片應咒言飄浮起來，瑩白的光暈包裹著破碎的骨筆。錐形筆尖打轉了幾圈之後，朝某個方向緩緩飛去。"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#11$1", "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來另一截骨筆離此處不遠。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#1$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "主任……", "name": "斯凱"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2039_1#7$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這確實有可能是個圈套，但我有不得不去的理由。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這支骨筆上……有我熟悉的咒言的痕跡。", "name": "娜斯提"}, "figure_art": "avg_4212_nasti_1#4$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 367, "